text: Viktorija Panchurova (; born 25 December 1999) is a Macedonian footballer who plays as a goalkeeper for 1. liga club ŽFK Tiverija Istatov and the North Macedonia women's national team. ==References== Category:1999 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football goalkeepers Category:Macedonian women's footballers Category:North Macedonia women's international footballers Category:KF Vllaznia Shkodër players Category:Macedonian expatriate footballers Category:Macedonian expatriate sportspeople in Albania Category:Expatriate footballers in Albania
title: Viktorija Panchurova
